{"tid":2305131,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"Kavinsky - Nightcall 廣東話版","createTime":"2020-11-29T11:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T19:29:18.000Z","uid":90660,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7c05b1d7693122d64d05de9e20f4a3ebad5a5f","tid":2305131,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MV_3Dpw-BRY&amp;ab_channel=RecordMakers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMV_3Dpw-BRY%26ab_channel%3DRecordMakers&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGidqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=e8ecd307\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MV_3Dpw-BRY&amp;ab_channel=RecordMakers</a><br />\n<br />\n改詞: 貓頭人<br />\n<br />\nI'm giving you a night call to tell you how I feel<br />\n我勸過你要遠去趁現在 別逗留<br />\nI want to drive you through the night, down the hills<br />\n靠倚在那破碎信念 就在旁<br />\nI'm gonna tell you something you don't want to hear<br />\n這羈絆看似會注定 像陌路人<br />\nI'm gonna show you where it's dark, but have no fear<br />\n借酒醉訴說到午夜 剩下寂寥<br />\n<br />\nThere something inside you<br />\n能否飛上半空<br />\nIt's hard to explain<br />\n橫跨天際線<br />\nThey're talking about you boy<br />\n迷失方向的導航<br />\nBut you're still the same<br />\n仍尋求著你"},{"pid":"f5a19d5fc2715b7422a3e3c59476ac893311b9f2","tid":2305131,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CILFtSxHkZy/?igshid=165wzc6h2xrst\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCILFtSxHkZy%2F%3Figshid%3D165wzc6h2xrst&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGidqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=3847a778\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCILFtSxHkZy%2F%3Figshid%3D165wzc6h2xrst&h=1dc6d788\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CILFtSxHkZy/?igshid=165wzc6h2xrst</a>"},{"pid":"b1dc4497a68cb7913aac41fab7981ec4353371ce","tid":2305131,